### Criar um ativo
POST http://localhost:8080/investments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ACAO",
  "symbol": "BBAS3",
  "quantity": 100,
  "purchasePrice": 19.68,
  "purchaseDate": "2025-07-31"
}

### Criar uma criptomoeda
POST http://localhost:8080/investments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CRIPTO",
